{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781081935745,"sessionID":"ses_14f3ef063ffeCcnT1C938V1BoI","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_0173qYSDLgnoNqUKandLxv1m","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/dheeraj/Downloads/refactor/bespoke-labs-tasks-01/rust-ls-core/solution/solve.sh"},"output":"<path>/Users/dheeraj/Downloads/refactor/bespoke-labs-tasks-01/rust-ls-core/solution/solve.sh</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: #!/bin/bash\n2: set -euo pipefail\n3: \n4: # Oracle marker: HARBOR_ORACLE_FLAG is injected only into oracle runs (via\n5: # [solution.env] in task.toml). test.sh matches this token to skip the anti-cheat\n6: # checks, since the oracle decrypts the baked oracle `ls` as its solution. The\n7: # agent never sees the flag, so it cannot forge this marker.\n8: echo \"${HARBOR_ORACLE_FLAG:-}\" > /app/.harbor_oracle_marker\n9: \n10: # Decrypt the oracle ls binary and use it as our solution.\n11: # The key matches what test.sh uses to decrypt for comparison.\n12: DECRYPT_KEY=\"r5tL5_v3r1f1er_k3y_8f2a\"\n13: \n14: openssl enc -d -aes-256-cbc -salt -pbkdf2 -iter 100000 \\\n15:     -in /app/.test_data/oracle.enc \\\n16:     -pass pass:$DECRYPT_KEY \\\n17:     -out /app/workspace/rls\n18: \n19: chmod +x /app/workspace/rls\n\n(End of file - total 19 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"#!/bin/bash\nset -euo pipefail\n\n# Oracle marker: HARBOR_ORACLE_FLAG is injected only into oracle runs (via\n# [solution.env] in task.toml). test.sh matches this token to skip the anti-cheat\n# checks, since the oracle decrypts the baked oracle `ls` as its solution. The\n# agent never sees the flag, so it cannot forge this marker.\necho \"${HARBOR_ORACLE_FLAG:-}\" > /app/.harbor_oracle_marker\n\n# Decrypt the oracle ls binary and use it as our solution.\n# The key matches what test.sh uses to decrypt for comparison.\nDECRYPT_KEY=\"r5tL5_v3r1f1er_k3y_8f2a\"\n\nopenssl enc -d -aes-256-cbc -salt -pbkdf2 -iter 100000 \\\n    -in /app/.test_data/oracle.enc \\\n    -pass pass:$DECRYPT_KEY \\\n    -out /app/workspace/rls\n\nchmod +x /app/workspace/rls","truncated":false,"loaded":[],"display":{"type":"file","path":"/Users/dheeraj/Downloads/refactor/bespoke-labs-tasks-01/rust-ls-core/solution/solve.sh","text":"#!/bin/bash\nset -euo pipefail\n\n# Oracle marker: HARBOR_ORACLE_FLAG is injected only into oracle runs (via\n# [solution.env] in task.toml). test.sh matches this token to skip the anti-cheat\n# checks, since the oracle decrypts the baked oracle `ls` as its solution. The\n# agent never sees the flag, so it cannot forge this marker.\necho \"${HARBOR_ORACLE_FLAG:-}\" > /app/.harbor_oracle_marker\n\n# Decrypt the oracle ls binary and use it as our solution.\n# The key matches what test.sh uses to decrypt for comparison.\nDECRYPT_KEY=\"r5tL5_v3r1f1er_k3y_8f2a\"\n\nopenssl enc -d -aes-256-cbc -salt -pbkdf2 -iter 100000 \\\n    -in /app/.test_data/oracle.enc \\\n    -pass pass:$DECRYPT_KEY \\\n    -out /app/workspace/rls\n\nchmod +x /app/workspace/rls","lineStart":1,"lineEnd":19,"totalLines":19,"truncated":false}},"title":"rust-ls-core/solution/solve.sh","time":{"start":1781081935724,"end":1781081935739}},"metadata":{"anthropic":{"caller":{"type":"direct"}}},"id":"prt_eb0c187f3001RuYX7JFAYXcrIs","sessionID":"ses_14f3ef063ffeCcnT1C938V1BoI","messageID":"msg_eb0c179450017YXZQ8drptmc6f"}}
