{"type":"text","timestamp":1781081976687,"sessionID":"ses_14f3ef063ffeCcnT1C938V1BoI","part":{"id":"prt_eb0c2239700154kKuB1Ws3lj4l","messageID":"msg_eb0c21af5001aIK3PM1hWidYyh","sessionID":"ses_14f3ef063ffeCcnT1C938V1BoI","type":"text","text":"Now I have enough context. Let me evaluate each check:\n\n**Dockerfile package analysis:**\n- `build-essential`, `gcc`, `g++`, `make`, `pkg-config` — needed for Rust crate builds with native deps (Cargo build under verifier)\n- `tmux`, `git`, `strace` — Harbor hard rules\n- `ca-certificates`, `curl` — needed for rustup install\n- `openssl` — used in test.sh & solve.sh for decrypt\n- `bc` — search test.sh: no usage found\n- `file` — used in test.sh for ELF check","time":{"start":1781081973655,"end":1781081976678}}}
